snippet.title: Super Bunny Man - V1.0 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello everyone!

Super Bunny Man is launching out of Early Access into V1.0 on 16th of May 2023! Hooray! 🎉

Embrace the carrot! 🥕
Become SUPER BUNNY MAN now! 🐰

🎮 Play on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/673750/Super_Bunny_Man/

💻 Website: https://www.superbunnyman.com
